README
======

Install & Run
-------------

Clone, buildout and fresh start::

    cd ~/work/afpy/pyconfr/
    hg clone https://florent@bitbucket.org/toopy/django-pyconfr
    virtualenv -p python2.7 --no-site-packages env
    source env/bin/activate
    cd django-pyconfr/
    pip install -U setuptools
    python bootstrap.py
    ./bin/django syncdb
    ./bin/django collectstatic
    ./bin/django runserver


Gunicorn start::

    ./bin/django run_gunicorn -b 127.0.0.1:8001

